        "content": [
          "German often uses ZU with infinitives:",
          "",
          "BASIC STRUCTURE:",
          "verb + ZU + infinitive",
          "",
          "Ich versuche zu schlafen. (I try to sleep)",
          "Es macht Spaß zu tanzen. (It's fun to dance)",
          "Ich habe keine Zeit zu kochen.",
          "(I have no time to cook)",
          "",
          "WITH SEPARABLE VERBS:",
          "ZU goes BETWEEN prefix and verb:",
          "",
          "aufzustehen (to get up)",
          "anzukommen (to arrive)",
          "",
          "Ich vergesse oft aufzustehen.",
          "(I often forget to get up)",
          "",
          "NO ZU with modal verbs or lassen!",
          "",
          "RELATED: 'sobald' (as soon as) is a conjunction",
          "that introduces time clauses."
        ],
        "pronunciation": "Lektion 50"
      }
